                             java.lang.String description,

        Returns a new roofing blueprint from the provided information.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the roofing to specify in the blueprint.
        description - The description of the roofing to specify in the blueprint.
        active - Whether or not the roofing to specify in the blueprint can be applied to orders.
